### CCR-028 (AT-06) — CC Game Settings Modal
###
### 검증:
### - PATCH 엔드포인트로 game settings 갱신
### - settings_kv router 활용

@host = http://localhost:8000
@admin_token = {{$dotenv ADMIN_JWT}}

### 35.1 GET /settings — 현재 KV 조회
GET {{host}}/api/v1/settings
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

# 예상: 200 + envelope { data: [SettingsKvOut[]], error: null }

### 35.2 PUT /settings — game settings 갱신
PUT {{host}}/api/v1/settings
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "key": "game.default_blind_structure_id",
  "value": "1"
}

# 예상: 200 + envelope { data: SettingsKvOut, error: null }
